'''Awlad Elias village''' is one of the villages of [[sodfa]] in [[Asyut Governorate]], [[Egypt]]. According to statistics from the year 2006, the total population in Awlad Elias was 16283 people, 8521 men and 7762 women.<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.msrintranet.capmas.gov.eg/pls/census/cnsest_a_sex_ama?LANG=1 |title = البيانات السكانية لمدينة أو قرية حسب تقديرات السكان 2006 |publisher = الجهاز المصري المركزي للإحصاء |language = Arabic |date = 12 أغسطس 2012 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/69rltRqYm?url=http://www.msrintranet.capmas.gov.eg/pls/census/cnsest_a_sex_ama?LANG=1&lname=1&YY=2006&cod=25&gv= |archivedate = 2012-08-12 |access-date = 2017-07-12 |df = }}</ref>
