The '''Isukha''', are a tribe of the [[Luhya people|Luhya]] nation of [[Kenya]]. Among the Luhya, the Isukha are known as ''Abiisukha''. They reside [[Kakamega District]] neighboured by the [[Idakho]] and the [[Tiriki]].
